/header><div class="section-head"><div><h2>选择服务</h2></div><p id="recommendText">正在匹配推荐方式</p></div><section class="grid" id="serviceGrid" aria-label="支付和好友入口"><article class="service-card mint" data-service="wechat-pay" id="wechat-pay"><div class="card-top"><div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7.8 5.2C4.6 5.2 2 7.3 2 9.9c0 1.5.9 2.9 2.3 3.8l-.6 2.2 2.5-1.3c.5.1 1 .2 1.6.2 3.2 0 5.8-2.1 5.8-4.9S11 5.2 7.8 5.2Z"/><path d="M13.8 9.4c3.3 0 6.2 2.2 6.2 5 0 1.5-.8 2.9-2.3 3.8l.5 2-2.3-1.2c-.7.2-1.3.3-2.1.3-3.3 0-6-2.2-6-4.9 0-.2 0-.4.1-.6"/><path d="M6.2 9.3h.01M9.3 9.3h.01M12.3 14h.01M15.8 14h.01"/></svg></div><span class="tag default">二维码</span><span class="tag recommend">当前推荐</span></div><h3>微信支付</h3><p class="desc">微信内长按识别收款码；另提供付款口令作为备用方式。</p><div class="account">收款人：下雪</div><div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" type="button" id="openWechatPay">打开微信付款</button><button class="btn secondary" type="button" id="wechatCodeButton">复制口令并打开微信</button></div></article><article class="service-card sky" data-service="alipay" id="alipay"><div class="card-top"><div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"/><path d="M7 8h10M9 5.8v4.4c0 3.5-1.3 6.1-3.2 7.7M8.4 12.2c2.7 2.1 5.7 3.6 9.6 4.5M10.8 11.5h6.8"/></svg></div><span class="tag default">直接跳转</span><span class="tag recommend">当前推荐</span></div><h3>支付宝付款</h3><p class="desc">普通浏览器或支付宝内可直接打开；微信内会提示切换浏览器。</p><div class="account">收款人：下雪工作室</div><div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" type="button" id="openAlipay">打开支付宝付款</button><button class="btn secondary" type="button" data-qr="alipay">查看支付宝二维码</button></div></article><article class="service-card peach" data-service="wechat-friend" id="wechat-friend"><div class="