ection class="sheet" id="qrSheet" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="qrTitle" hidden><div class="sheet-panel"><div class="sheet-head"><div class="sheet-title"><h2 id="qrTitle">二维码</h2><p id="qrSubtitle">长按图片识别</p></div><button class="close" type="button" data-close="qrSheet" aria-label="关闭">×</button></div><div class="qr-wrap"><img class="qr-image" id="qrImage" src="" alt="二维码"></div><div class="sheet-foot"><p class="sheet-hint" id="qrHint">请长按图片并选择识别二维码。</p><button class="btn" type="button" data-close="qrSheet">完成</button></div></div></section><section class="sheet" id="wechatGuide" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="wechatGuideTitle" hidden><div class="sheet-panel"><div class="sheet-head"><div class="sheet-title"><h2 id="wechatGuideTitle">需要在微信中完成</h2><p id="wechatGuideSubtitle">已尝试唤醒微信</p></div><button class="close" type="button" data-close="wechatGuide" aria-label="关闭">×</button></div><div class="guide-body"><p class="guide-lead" id="wechatGuideLead">若微信没有自动打开，请按以下步骤继续。</p><div class="steps"><div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div><h3 id="wechatStepOneTitle">所需内容已复制</h3><p id="wechatStepOneText">无需再次长按复制。</p></div></div><div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div><h3>打开微信</h3><p>可点击下方按钮再次发起打开微信请求。</p></div></div><div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div><h3 id="wechatStepThreeTitle">在微信中粘贴并打开</h3><p id="wechatStepThreeText">粘贴到文件传输助手或聊天窗口后继续。</p></div></div></div><div class="guide-actions"><button class="btn" type="button" id="retryWechat">再次打开微信</button><button class="btn" type="button" id="wechatGuideQr">直接查看二维码</button></div></div></div></section><section class="sheet" id="alipayGuide" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="guideTitle" hidden><div class="sheet-panel"><div class="sheet-head"><div class="sheet-title"><h2 id="guideTitle">在浏览器中打开支付宝</h2><p>微信内可能阻止支付宝链接</p></div><button class="close" type="button" data-close="alipayGuide" aria-label="关闭">×</button></div><div class="guide-body"><p 